== /fly ==

=== Basics ===

//Toggles creative flymode for yourself or a player//

**Usage:** /fly (player)

**Permission Nodes**
 * rcmds.fly
 * rcmds.others.fly

=== In Depth ===

{{{/fly}}} toggles the ability to use creative fly mode on and off for the sender or {{{(player)}}} if specified and
the sender has {{{rcmds.others.fly}}}.

This command supports [[../name-completion.html|online name-completion]].

=== Examples ===

{{{/fly}}} - Toggles fly mode for the sender.\\
{{{/fly Notch}}} - Toggles fly mode for {{{Notch}}}.